This adapter controls the [http://www.sutter.com/ Sutter] [http://www.sutter.com/products/product_sheets/Lambda_DG-4.html DG4] and [http://www.sutter.com/products/imaging.html other hardware] through the Lambda 10 family of controllers.  This includes the
* Lambda 10-2 (Wheels A and B and Shutters A and B)
* Lambda 10-3 (Wheels A, B, and C and Shutters A and B), and SC (Shutter A).
* Lambda 10-C

Currently, only the serial interface to these devices (not parallel port or USB) has been implemented.

